//                    for a short-lived session token.
//   * Heartbeat    — proves liveness; learns of config changes + drain orders.
//   * ReportMetrics— streams resource pressure for scheduling + dashboards.
//   * RefreshToken — rotates the session token before it expires.
//   * RunStream    — bidi: the control-plane PUSHES run assignments down the
//                    tunnel; the agent reports acceptance + status + results.
//
